//About Page Learn About Swords This application was set up, not only for the residents of Swords but for the new and propestive residents in the future. The Swords App features provide a one-stop-shop for any resident to plan their next meal out in the town, or perhaps look up their bus times. The Swords app also provides bespoke data that make for interesting reading for local residents or maybe prospective house buyers. Our data can allow for a prospective house buyer to view data about Swords in a concise and easy manner. Users of our app can few data about all the Schools in Swords, Such as the boy to girl ratios. They can view the Crime data in Swords which will allow prospective house buyers or local residents to make descison is Swords a safe place to bring up a family. Users of the Swords App can also view data on the number of road accidents that have happened within Swords. This data is pulled from an API with the data being pulled from a Government Data Portal known as data.gov. LEARN MORE SIGN UP USERNAME PASSWORD LOGIN About Learn what the app is about
